---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Jiazhen Zhu" description="Jiazhen Zhu — 15+ years building data and AI products at major tech companies.">
  <header class="mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
    <img
      src="/avatar.jpeg"
      alt="Jiazhen Zhu"
      class="w-32 h-32 rounded-xl object-cover shrink-0"
    />
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">About</h1>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
        Currently at <strong style="color: var(--text);">Airbnb</strong>.
        Previously at <strong style="color: var(--text);">Capital One</strong> and
        <strong style="color: var(--text);">Walmart Global Tech</strong>.
        MBA from <strong style="color: var(--text);">NYU Stern</strong>.
        MS in Analytics from <strong style="color: var(--text);">Georgia Tech</strong>.
        Adjunct faculty at <strong style="color: var(--text);">Northeastern University</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="prose-custom">
    <p>
      I'm Jiazhen Zhu. I've spent 15+ years building data and AI products —
      from designing production ML pipelines to leading data platform teams.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Focus On</h2>
    <p>
      My day-to-day is at the intersection of AI systems and real-world delivery —
      getting from a working prototype to something that runs reliably in production.
      I write about what that actually looks like, because most writing on AI stops at the demo.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
      Over 15 years I've designed production ML pipelines, led data platform teams,
      and shipped AI-powered products used by millions of people at Airbnb, Capital One,
      and Walmart. That's given me a pattern library of what actually breaks when
      organizations try to move fast with AI — and what quietly works.
    </p>

    <h2>Writing & Research</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=P8PXzzoAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jiazhen-zhu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://medium.com/@JiazhenZhu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Medium</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://substack.com/@jiazhenzhu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Substack</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/jason-jz-zhu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
